		<legis-type>A BILL</legis-type>
		<official-title>To sustain the economic development and recreational use
		  of National Forest System land and other public land in the State of Montana,
		  to add certain land to the National Wilderness Preservation System, to release
		  certain wilderness study areas, to designate new areas for recreation, and for
		  other purposes.</official-title>
	</form>
	<legis-body>
