			 title; table of contents</header>
			<subsection id="idF7E834E4299B460491BAF072FE6A3203"><enum>(a)</enum><header>Short
			 title</header><text>This Act may be cited as the <quote><short-title>Forest Jobs and Recreation Act of
			 2009</short-title></quote>.</text>
			</subsection><subsection id="id1F1747B8839C4F6E8F6A0348F33D163D"><enum>(b)</enum><header>Table of
			 contents</header><text>The table of contents for this Act is as follows:</text>
