			 <quote>Centennial Mountains Wilderness</quote>.</text>
					</paragraph><paragraph id="id9218C1C9CCD847C5B12BF703F180C3C0"><enum>(3)</enum><header>Farlin Creek
			 wilderness</header><text>Certain land under the jurisdiction of the Dillon
